From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Date: Mon, 16 Feb 2026 17:42:59 +1100
Subject: [PATCH] drm: cix: Add Sky1 display drivers

Add Linlon Display Processor (DPU), Trilinear DP TX subsystem,
virtual display connector, PS185 DP-to-HDMI bridge support,
hotplug state machine, PSR, and suspend/resume handling.
