@@ -0,0 +1,246 @@
+//------------------------------------------------------------------------------
+//  COPYRIGHT (c) 2018-2022 TRILINEAR TECHNOLOGIES, INC.
+//  CONFIDENTIAL AND PROPRIETARY
+//
+//  THE SOURCE CODE CONTAINED HEREIN IS PROVIDED ON AN "AS IS" BASIS.
